name: Global X Enhanced S&P 500 Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide, to the extent reasonably possible and net of expenses: (a) exposure to the performance of the large-cap market segment of the U.S. equity market; and (b) high monthly distributions of dividend and call option income. To generate income, the ETF will be exposed to a dynamic covered call option writing program. The ETF will be exposed to a dynamic covered call option writing program.
